{"iti1:0.1":"Itivuttaka 1 ","iti1:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","iti1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti1:0.4":"Lobhasutta ","iti1:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti1:2.1":"“Ekadhammam, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ","iti1:2.2":"aham vo patibhogo anagamitaya. ","iti1:2.3":"Katamam ekadhammam? ","iti1:2.4":"Lobham, bhikkhave, ekadhammam pajahatha; ","iti1:2.5":"aham vo patibhogo anagamitaya”ti. ","iti1:2.6":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti1:2.7":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti1:3.1":"“Yena lobhena luddhase, ","iti1:3.2":"satta gacchanti duggatim; ","iti1:3.3":"Tam lobham sammadannaya, ","iti1:3.4":"pajahanti vipassino; ","iti1:3.5":"Pahaya na punayanti, ","iti1:3.6":"imam lokam kudacanan”ti. ","iti1:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti1:4.2":"Pathamam. "}